  "description": "I worked on the frontend with integration plugins for Acronis services: Kaseya VSA, Kaseya BMS, Tiger Paw, Auto Task, ConnectWise, Cloud Blue, Datto. Each integration was covered by tests at more than 80%. I also worked on creating an internal library for working with the API and on an integration constructor. The integration constructor is a pure JS library that creates any frontend app using a JSON file. We created 2 apps: first — an easy editor with a visual constructor of the needed result; second — a renderer of the app from a JSON file (with framework-agnostic principles). We created a Vue.js renderer for the library. I also worked on e2e tests for Acronis written in TestCafe, and I developed a Node proxy-server utility for getting mocks of API requests for TestCafe e2e tests.",
